1. create a types.ts for every functionality types that needs to be shared.
 example:
 Profile/
        Profile.tsx
        index.ts
        types.ts

2. create a utils.ts for utility functions that needs to be shared for that functionality
example:
 Profile/
        Content/
            Account.tsx
            utils.ts
            Settings.tsx
        Profile.tsx
        index.ts
        utils.ts
        types.ts
3. Only create variable functions using const.
example: const flattenTreeItems = () => {}

4. Always use type instead of interfaces

5. Make use of @catalystone/utils package for shared utilities. for types, functions and components for re-use